title: Welcome to the Course
description: Introduction to the course curriculum, instructor background, and what you'll learn throughout this bootcamp.

title: Setting Up Development Environment
description: Install Node.js, MongoDB, VS Code, and essential extensions. Set up your first MERN project.

title: Creating RESTful APIs with Express
description: Learn to build scalable REST APIs using Express.js, middleware, routing, and error handling.

title: MongoDB Database Design
description: Understanding NoSQL concepts, schema design, and CRUD operations with Mongoose.

title: React Components and Props
description: Build reusable React components, understand props, and component composition.

title: State Management with Redux
description: Master Redux for state management in large React applications.

title: Custom Hooks and Performance Optimization
description: Create custom hooks, memoization techniques, and React performance best practices.

title: NumPy and Pandas Basics
description: Work with arrays, dataframes, and data manipulation using NumPy and Pandas libraries.

title: Linear Regression and Decision Trees
description: Implement your first machine learning models from scratch and using scikit-learn.
